      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must hold ISO 9001 certification and version-controlled release documentation.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 is used under an ISO 9001-certified QMS. Release notes, regression test suite results, and version control logs were reviewed and found compliant with the required level."
