      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must pass published benchmark problems for rotating-machinery incompressible flow with documented order-of-accuracy confirmation.",
      "rationale": "Taylor-Green vortex and lid-driven cavity benchmarks were reproduced; second-order spatial accuracy confirmed. Results archived in the project verification report VR-2025-07."
    },
    {
