      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be below 5% for the hemolysis index QoI on the nominal geometry.",
      "rationale": "Three systematically refined meshes (2.1 M, 6.4 M, 18.7 M cells) were evaluated. Richardson extrapolation yields GCI = 3.2% for the relative hemolysis index, meeting the 5% threshold."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
